quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  54,9,"kdhdhabt qabl qawmak -ayha alrswl- qawm nuh fkdhdhabu eabdana nwhana, wqalu: hu mjnwn, wanthrwh mutawaeidin 'iiaah bi'anwae aladha، 'iin lam yantah ean dewth"
  54,10,"fdea nuh rabah anni daeif ean muqawamatan hwla', fantasir li beqab min eindik ealaa kufruhum bk"
  54,11,"fajbna dea'h, fafatahna 'abwab alsama' bima' kthyr mtdfq, wshqqna al'ard eywnana mtfjrt balma', faltaqaa ma'an alsama' wama' al'ard ealaa 'ihlakhm aldhy qddarh allah lhm; jaza'an shrkhm"
  54,12,"fajbna dea'h, fafatahna 'abwab alsama' bima' kthyr mtdfq, wshqqna al'ard eywnana mtfjrt balma', faltaqaa ma'an alsama' wama' al'ard ealaa 'ihlakhm aldhy qddarh allah lhm; jaza'an shrkhm"
  54,13,"whmlna nwhana wman maeah ealaa safinat dhat 'alwah wmsamyr shuddat bha, tajri bmraa minaa whfz, wa'aghraqna almkdhbyn; jaza'an lahum ealaa kufruhum wantsarana lnwh ealayh alsalam. wafi hdha dalil ealaa 'iithbat sifat aleynyn lilah subhanah wteala, kama ylyq bh"
  54,14,"whmlna nwhana wman maeah ealaa safinat dhat 'alwah wmsamyr shuddat bha, tajri bmraa minaa whfz, wa'aghraqna almkdhbyn; jaza'an lahum ealaa kufruhum wantsarana lnwh ealayh alsalam. wafi hdha dalil ealaa 'iithbat sifat aleynyn lilah subhanah wteala, kama ylyq bh"
  54,15,"wlqd abqyna qisat nuh mae qawmih eibratan wdlyla ealaa qdrtna liman baed nwh; lyetbru wytezu bima hll bhdhh al'umat alty kafart brbha, fahal min mtez ytez? fakayf kan eadhabi wndhry liman kafar bi wakadhab rsly, walam ytez bima ja'at bh? 'iinah kan ezymana mwlmana"
  54,16,"wlqd abqyna qisat nuh mae qawmih eibratan wdlyla ealaa qdrtna liman baed nwh; lyetbru wytezu bima hll bhdhh al'umat alty kafart brbha, fahal min mtez ytez? fakayf kan eadhabi wndhry liman kafar bi wakadhab rsly, walam ytez bima ja'at bh? 'iinah kan ezymana mwlmana"
  54,17,"wlqd sahhalna lfz alquran lltlawt walhfz, wmeanyh llfhm waltdbr, liman 'arad 'an yatadhakar wyetbr, fahal min mtez bh?"
  54,18,"kdhbt ead hwdana feaqbnahm, fakayf kan eadhabi lahum ealaa kfrhm, wndhry ealaa takdhib rswlhm, wedm al'iiman bh? 'iinah kan ezymana mwlmana"
  54,19,"'inna 'arsalna ealayhim ryhana shadidat albrd, fi yawm shwm mustamirun ealayhim bialeadhab walhlak, taqtalie alnaas min mwadehm ealaa al'ard ftrmy bihim ealaa rwwshm, ftdq aenaqhm, wyfsl rwwshm ean ajsadhm, fttrkhm kalnkhl almnqle min aslh"
  54,20,"'inna 'arsalna ealayhim ryhana shadidat albrd, fi yawm shwm mustamirun ealayhim bialeadhab walhlak, taqtalie alnaas min mwadehm ealaa al'ard ftrmy bihim ealaa rwwshm, ftdq aenaqhm, wyfsl rwwshm ean ajsadhm, fttrkhm kalnkhl almnqle min aslh"
  54,21,"fkyf kan eadhabi wndhry liman kafar by, wkdhdhab rusuli walam yumin bhm? 'iinah kan ezymana mwlmana"
  54,22,"wlqd sahhalna lfz alquran lltlawt walhfz, wmeanyh llfhm wlltdbr, liman 'arad 'an yatadhakar wyetbr, fahal min mtez bh? wafi hdha hthth ealaa alastkthar min tlawt alquran wtelmh wtelymh"
  54,23,"kdhbt thamud -whm qawm salh- bialayat alty 'undhriu bha, fqalu: abshrana minaa wahdana natabieuh nahn aljamaeat alkathirat wahu wahd? 'iinaa 'iidhana lafi bued ean alswab wjnwn"
  54,24,"kdhbt thamud -whm qawm salh- bialayat alty 'undhriu bha, fqalu: abshrana minaa wahdana natabieuh nahn aljamaeat alkathirat wahu wahd? 'iinaa 'iidhana lafi bued ean alswab wjnwn"
  54,25,"a'unzl ealayh alwhy wkhuss balnbwt min bynna, wahu wahid mna? bal hu kthyr alkadhib waltjbr. sayarwn eind nuzul aleadhab bihim fi aldunya wayawm alqiamat man alkadhaab almtjbr?"
  54,26,"a'unzl ealayh alwhy wkhuss balnbwt min bynna, wahu wahid mna? bal hu kthyr alkadhib waltjbr. sayarwn eind nuzul aleadhab bihim fi aldunya wayawm alqiamat man alkadhaab almtjbr?"
  54,27,"'ina mkhrjw alnaaqat alty salwha min alskhrt; akhtbarana lhm, fantzr- ya salh- ma yhll bihim min aledhab, wastabir ealaa daewatak 'iiahum wadhahm lk"
  54,28,"wakhbrhm 'ana alma' maqsum bayn qawmak walnaqt: llnaqt ywm, walahum ywm, kulu shirb yahduruh man kanat qsmth, wyuhzr ealaa min lays bqsmt lh"
  54,29,"fnadu sahibahum balhd ealaa eqrha, ftnawl alnaaqat bydh, fnhrha feaqabtuhm, fakayf kan eqaby lahum ealaa kfrhm, w'indhary liman esa rsly?"
  54,30,"fnadu sahibahum balhd ealaa eqrha, ftnawl alnaaqat bydh, fnhrha feaqabtuhm, fakayf kan eqaby lahum ealaa kfrhm, w'indhary liman esa rsly?"
  54,31,"'ina 'arsalna ealayhim jbryl, fsah bihim sayhatan wahdt, fbadu ean akhrhm, fakanuu kalzre alyabs aldhy yujel hizarana ealaa al'iibil walmwashy"
  54,32,"wlqd sahhalna lfz alquran lltlawt walhfz, wmeanyh llfhm waltdbr liman 'arad 'an yatadhakar wyetbr, fahal min mtez bh?"
  54,33,kdhdhabt qawm lut biayat allah alati andhiru bha
  54,34,"'ina 'arsalna ealayhim hjartan 'iilaa al lwt, njjaynahm min aleadhab fi akhir allyl, niematan min eindina elyhm, kama athbna lwtana walh wanemna elyhm, fa'anjaynahum min edhabna, nuthyb man aman bina wshkrna"
  54,35,"'ina 'arsalna ealayhim hjartan 'iilaa al lwt, njjaynahm min aleadhab fi akhir allyl, niematan min eindina elyhm, kama athbna lwtana walh wanemna elyhm, fa'anjaynahum min edhabna, nuthyb man aman bina wshkrna"
  54,36,"wlqd khwwaf lut qawmih bas allah wedhabh, falam yasmaeuu lh, bal shkku fi dhlk, wkdhdhabwh"
  54,37,"wlqd talabuu minh 'an yafealuu alfahishat biduyufih min almlaykt, fatamasna 'aeyunahum falam yubsru shyyana, fqyl lhm: dhuquu eadhabi w'indhary aldhy 'undhirukum bih lut ealayh alslam"
  54,38,"wlqd ja'ahum waqt alsabah eadhab dayim aistaqara fihim hataa yufdy bihim 'iilaa eadhab alakhrt, wdhlk aleadhab hu rjmhm bialhijarat waqalb qurahm wajaeal aelaha asflha, fqyl lhm: dhuquu eadhabi aldhy anzlth bkm; lkfrkm wtkdhybkm, w'indhary aldhy 'undhirukum bih lut ealayh alslam"
  54,39,"walaqad ja'ahum waqt alsabah eadhab dayim aistaqara fihim hataa yufdy bihim 'iilaa eadhab alakhrt, wdhlk aleadhab hu rjmhm bialhijarat waqalb qurahm wajaeal aelaha asflha, fqyl lhm: dhuquu eadhabi aldhy anzlth bkm; lkfrkm wtkdhybkm, w'indhary aldhy 'undhirukum bih lut ealayh alslam"
  54,40,"wlqd sahhalna lfz alquran lltlawt walhfz, wmeanyh llfhm waltdbr liman 'arad 'an ytdhkr, fahal min mtez bh?"
  54,41,wlqd ja' atbae fireawn wqwmah 'indharuna baleqwbt lahum ealaa kfrhm
  54,42,"kdhdhabu badltna klha aldalt ealaa whdanytna wnbwt anbyayna, feaqbnahm bialeadhab euqubat eaziz la yghalab, muqtadir ealaa ma ysha'"
  54,43,"akfarkm- ya maeshar qrysh- khayr min aladhin tqddam dhikrihim mmn hlku bsbb tkdhybhm, 'am lakum bara'at min eiqab allah fi alkutub almnzlt ealaa al'anbia' balslamt min aleqwb?"
  54,44,"bl ayqwl kafaar \"mk\": nahn 'uwlu hzm waray wa'umirna mjtme, fnhn jamaeat muntasiratan la yghlbna min aradna bsw'?"
  54,45,"syhzm jame kafaar \"mk\" 'amam almwmnyn, wywllun aladbar, waqad hadath hdha yawm \"bdr"
  54,46,"walsaet maweidahum aldhy yujazwn fih bima ysthqwn, walsaaeat 'aezam waqsa mimaa lhqhm min aleadhab yawm \"bdr"
  54,47,"'in almujrimin fi tyh ean alhaqu wena' wedhab. yawm yujrrun fi alnaar ealaa wjwhhm, wyqal lhm: dhuquu shdt eadhab jhnm"
  54,48,"'in almujrimin fi tyh ean alhaqu wena' wedhab. yawm yujrrun fi alnaar ealaa wjwhhm, wyqal lhm: dhuquu shdt eadhab jhnm"
  54,49,"'inna kula shay' khalaqnah bimiqdar qadarnah wqdynah, wasabaq ealimna bh, wktabtna lah fi allwh almhfwz"
  54,50,"wma 'amrina llshy' 'iidha 'aradnah 'iilaa 'an naqul qwlt wahidatan wahi \"kn\", fayakun kalamh albsr, la yata'akhar trft eyn"
  54,51,"wlqd 'ahlakna ashbahkm fi alkufr min al'umam alkhalyt, fahal min mtez bima hll bihim min alnnakal waledhab?"
  54,52,wkl shay' faealah ashbahkm almadwn min khayr 'aw shrr maktub fi alkutub alty ktbtha alhfzt
  54,53,"wakulu saghir wakabir min 'aemalahum musattar fi shayfhm, wsyjazwn bh"
  54,54,"'in almutaqin fi basatin ezymt, wa'anhar wasieat yawm alqyamt"
  54,55,"fy majlis hq, laa laghw fih wala tathim eind allah almalik alezym, alkhaliq llashya' klha, almqtdr ealaa kl shay' tabarak wteala"